{"tid":5631,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個代表到香港嘅食物","createTime":"2016-11-27T03:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-27T12:55:46.000Z","uid":19386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"826c549a948b5b2d05f678b9d81c79ada2a56d60","tid":5631,"uid":19386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T03:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6cLK9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6cLK9e.jpg&h=337a88f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先一定係車仔麵！<br />\n<br />\n本身香港俾人感覺已經係有少少麻甩，車仔麵完完全全體現到麻甩嘅精髓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n車仔麵起源於香港，一過左境，深圳澳門已經冇得食咁濟。有獨特性，有歷史，亦深受港人愛戴。啱啱落嚟香港嘅新移民，會對車仔麵冇乜情意結，但土生土長嘅香港人，就一定對車仔麵有一份情懷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再者，揀擇嘅香港人可以喺車仔麵嘅配搭系統中揀啱自己想食嘅野，由麵類、餸、湯、辣度、以至配菜，完完全全自己揀，試問仲有邊樣野食可以咁就到香港人？<br />\n<br />\n個人認為香港車仔麵嘅地位係媲美日本拉麵，絕對係香港嘅代表食物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e095da38225f56c60c81bb2e0add42c6505721","tid":5631,"uid":5751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T03:48:05.000Z","msg":"雞"},{"pid":"471dcd4368f4a189386a5f44d3eeb46f4599a33d","tid":5631,"uid":5797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T03:52:32.000Z","msg":"外國人唔會識叫<br />\n佢係地道食物因爲比到香港人有選擇"},{"pid":"e0feaa50647f4bcd8ba7730683d7413e5bcb7585","tid":5631,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T03:58:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/27/115649_34e922a0deecb598800da5a2f0f61f64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F27%2F115649_34e922a0deecb598800da5a2f0f61f64.jpg&h=57dca53d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9007e7678eca55bfb168e6171c70246bee3e4ad0","tid":5631,"uid":16886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T04:00:26.000Z","msg":"細蓉<br />\n蛋撻"},{"pid":"4cd5789d2552d3b5722e21d5b8787a01e6b04ac9","tid":5631,"uid":3128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T04:02:59.000Z","msg":"雞蛋仔，格仔餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/27/120252_468c52f455295677f52ae00c6eeb7eba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F27%2F120252_468c52f455295677f52ae00c6eeb7eba.jpg&h=c293ad9d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/efk8b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fefk8b8.jpg&h=93643925&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0efa58cf71d7371fec57527a2e212b3d50023dc","tid":5631,"uid":19386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T04:05:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雞蛋仔，格仔餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/27/120252_468c52f455295677f52ae00c6eeb7eba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F27%2F120252_468c52f455295677f52ae00c6eeb7eba.jpg&h=b0bd8bfa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://na.cx/i/efk8b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fefk8b8.jpg&h=15bfc5b8&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌，好撚想食格仔餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc95f18c63672c6b1b9ff0fb893773e52fffb933","tid":5631,"uid":21611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T04:07:15.000Z","msg":"譚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56bab4ead18b9ee197df0d32f52d317bfc5f9e91","tid":5631,"uid":19386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T04:10:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>譚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我早幾日係旺角譚仔見到pair鬼佬鬼婆，睇住佢地好興奮咁叫野食，碗米線一嚟到，食到那口那面，食左幾淡就走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔識欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a01892248de8b5f972e39769d6d30df6ba13d0b4","tid":5631,"uid":19692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T04:11:52.000Z","msg":"燒味飯"},{"pid":"fde89488c6ed96854bd89e4525b7f8c502a12d40","tid":5631,"uid":8265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T10:47:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>譚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我早幾日係旺角譚仔見到pair鬼佬鬼婆，睇住佢地好興奮咁叫野食，碗米線一嚟到，食到那口那面，食左幾淡就走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔識欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地究竟係睇左咩guide 先會咁興奮想試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dad06fb8a09690926395dcc6472527ed8c917479","tid":5631,"uid":9629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T12:55:46.000Z","msg":"雲吞麵算唔算？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}